{"tid":1305133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲點解可以咁放肆 入黎睇睇你就知","createTime":"2019-07-10T19:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T17:47:19.000Z","uid":137502,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e824cc8b2f001d24a096cd06d7657f2252fda2","tid":1305133,"uid":137502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:24:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為我地抗爭者仲有包伏 仲有底線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n人地根本好似港共政府無底線咁欺壓你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而你地就長期set底線俾自己 話好暴力 我地咁樣同佢地冇分別 覺得和平冷靜就可以令佢地知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njhntzK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnjhntzK.jpg&h=e470c7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲惡咁多 使鬼理你地冷靜又和平嘅暴徒咩 其實我地係佢地心目中都冠上左暴徒依個名 係要堅持打造一個聖人嘅形象係無用架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地點解驚共產黨唔係無原因 比起你班所謂暴徒 港共政府嘅惡行可怕得多啦 使驚你地？ 啲暴徒車尾燈都見唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pWfOC6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pWfOC6.png&h=862c3c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家我地根本唔能夠利用合法 正常 和平 或者付出代價較少嘅渠道反應意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭根本唔應該有底線 如果依個政權無底線咁欺壓人民 咁點解我地要畫一條底線俾自己 然後跟政權講 我地去到依一度就會點到即止 this is ridiculous <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHVz4gi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHVz4gi.jpg&h=54c1e725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人請放棄所有嘅底線 所有包伏 無任何底線 抗爭者先會令人可怕 令藍絲可怕 令共產黨可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所有一切都係梁天琦教曉我 附上梁天琦中文bbc訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C0zvv5f8p2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC0zvv5f8p2Q&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=b06a02b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C0zvv5f8p2Q</a>"},{"pid":"0e16b6a8868e6dcb7826d2c502eba1010bb2a31d","tid":1305133,"uid":137502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:28:21.000Z","msg":"我希望梁天琦嘅概念可以遍佈全港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc335c10bc2a869a0945af9ede23a4541171109","tid":1305133,"uid":137502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:30:07.000Z","msg":"如用這歌可以代表我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f10d3cb8326b9d712a158d16164e371c0305805","tid":1305133,"uid":200739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:32:59.000Z","msg":"[推上熱門]hkcc編委會:六四血腥清場合情合理 學生抵罰 中共做法正確<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304975</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手share"},{"pid":"97257f82ec27336cf9ac6ac5946be06b41c437a1","tid":1305133,"uid":128065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:57:05.000Z","msg":"錯手負皮左樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"ef81582cec966e865fb2e46796b14c31d1c0fdd8","tid":1305133,"uid":128065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:58:21.000Z","msg":"唔洗再做聖人啦 班廢老只會不留手 話撚知你死 因為佢地跟本唔識思考"},{"pid":"294a21734055e01f858c5a1f0ef19faf1152001f","tid":1305133,"uid":2